Name: [DATA]{{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.lead_name }}[/DATA]
Source: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.source }}
Their message: [DATA]{{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.lead_message }}[/DATA]

PROPERTY THEY ARE ASKING ABOUT:
Address: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.property_address }}
Price: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.price_range }}
Beds: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.beds }}
Baths: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.baths }}
Key details: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.key_details }}

Write a short, warm, personal response from {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.agent_name }} to the lead. Requirements:
- Address them by first name
- Acknowledge what they asked about specifically
- Confirm the property is something you can help with
- Invite them to connect — suggest a quick call or showing
- Sign off with your name and phone number: {{ $node["Receive Lead"].json.body.agent_phone }}
- Keep it under 120 words — this is going via email
- Warm and human, not corporate or scripted
- IMPORTANT: If the lead asks a specific question (HOA fees, roof age, basement, inspection, lot size, etc.) that is not covered in the property details above, do NOT guess or invent an answer. Acknowledge the question briefly and tell them you will check on it and get back to them.

Return ONLY the message text. No labels, no subject line, no formatting markers.

